	   - vortex_tls_verify_cert

2013-06-07  Francis Brosnan Blázquez  <francis@aspl.es>

	* [fix] More updates into the frame reading engine..

	* [fix] Some changes to detect frame seqno mismatch..

	* [fix] Making internal frame getter to return the current list of frames   found when found not enough content to be keep on proceesing frames instead   of returning null.

	* [fix] Adding more debug information when found frame join failures..

2013-06-06  Francis Brosnan Blázquez  <francis@aspl.es>

	* [fix] Fixed support to receive incomplete BEEP frames and to retry   later with safety.

	* [fix] Fixed bug while reading several consolidated frames but where the   last frame received in just a part of the header. Added code to save those   bytes and retry later.

	libaxl: * [fix] Closing release..

2013-06-05  Francis Brosnan Blázquez  <francis@aspl.es>

	libaxl: * [fix] Updated compilation process to allow having it for   win64 and win32.

