	libvortex-1.1: * [fix] Fixings to make vortex to compile on windows...

	libvortex-1.1: * [fix] Updated vortex channel pool internals to detect if a   channel is ready by using vortex_channel_is_ready rather   vortex_channel_is_up_to_date.

